# 04 — Analytics and Reporting

## Workflow Overview
1. Data collection from ad platforms (Google, Meta, TikTok…)
2. Data validation and error detection
3. Data integration into BI tools (Power BI, Looker Studio, Tableau)
4. Building dashboards and automated reports
5. Presenting insights to decision-makers

## Common Tasks
- Data cleaning and normalization
- Segmentation by platform, campaign, geography, device
- Monitoring trends and anomalies
- Attribution analysis (last-click vs multi-touch)
- Budget pacing and forecasting

## Best Practices
- Maintain naming conventions for campaigns
- Validate data regularly to detect discrepancies
- Focus on actionable insights, not just numbers
- Visualize KPIs in context (trend lines, benchmarks, targets)
